{"tid":1892643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ff系列 - 想炒營(營地炒賣師)","createTime":"2020-02-22T16:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T08:53:35.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80648b4ea6a2d35161ff228c04e6685c5bd6d4cf","tid":1892643,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"有冇漁護想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/84411135_2733221546768598_8678167166018650112_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=V_bPGzShCi4AX-9-Oaw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=7c4f5eb1e789cae80ee7e028dbf20ae5&amp;oe=5EF59E6B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F84411135_2733221546768598_8678167166018650112_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ohc%3DV_bPGzShCi4AX-9-Oaw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D7c4f5eb1e789cae80ee7e028dbf20ae5%26oe%3D5EF59E6B&h=a01b2e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>【營地爆滿🈵🈵🈵】<br />\n北區鶴藪、新娘潭路涌背及西貢大網仔營地現時已經有好多人露營，預計爆滿嘅情況會喺嚟緊嘅周末出現。另外，鶴藪營地洗手間仍需關閉作緊急維修 ，洗手間設施同供水會暫停。計劃喺周末露營嘅朋友，可以考慮其他指定露營地點。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示 👉：因新型冠狀病毒在香港的情況，大家去郊野公園露營時，記得要注意個人衛生及妥善處理垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n郊野公園露營地點：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.afcd.gov.hk/&hellip;/cou_vis_cam_&hellip;/cou_vis_cam_cam.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fcou_vis_cam_%E2%80%A6%2Fcou_vis_cam_cam.html&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=2bad9bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.afcd.gov.hk/&hellip;/cou_vis_cam_&hellip;/cou_vis_cam_cam.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd524bee340cfafe52909aec07b23c055810d7f7","tid":1892643,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"有冇隔離營？"},{"pid":"8c979fe58bb1238d6cc514e004ebe324ea0b2ba6","tid":1892643,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi